<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Doğrulama Başarılı — BGT Market</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="3;url=/login?verified=1" />
    <style>
        body { background-color: #f8f4ec; font-family: sans-serif; }
        .success-card { border-radius: 20px; max-width: 500px; width: 100%; }
        .loader {
            border: 4px solid #f3f3f3;
            border-top: 4px solid #5a189a;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        @keyframes spin { 0% { transform: rotate(0deg); } 100% { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="min-height: 100vh;">
        <div class="card success-card shadow border-0 p-5 text-center">
            <div style="font-size: 5rem;">🎉</div>
            <h2 class="fw-bold mt-3" style="color: #24113b;">Doğrulama Tamamlandı!</h2>
            <p class="text-muted mt-2">Hesabınız başarıyla aktifleştirildi.</p>
            
            <div class="mt-4">
                <div class="loader me-2"></div>
                <p class="d-inline-block text-secondary">Giriş sayfasına yönlendiriliyorsunuz...</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-3">
                <small class="text-muted">Yönlendirme gerçekleşmezse <a href="/login?verified=1" style="color: #5a189a;">buraya tıklayın</a>.</small>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>